webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Portrait of Chambers Nils Magnus Winnerstrand. Born in the parish of Rök in 1804, he appeared to live most of his life in Lköpping. From 1848 married to Maria Christina Hagberg. The couple came to own the estate of St. Kors No. 18, at the corner of Apotekaregatan and Nydalen. He became a widower in 1868, and came to live as such for another 20 years - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMEA0001240112. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021017436819. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
